WEBVTT

00:04:28.867 --> 00:04:30.767
especially across generations,

00:04:31.648 --> 00:04:33.910
I realized I was opening a space

00:04:33.934 --> 00:04:36.922
for people to talk about things
that really mattered to them.

00:04:38.269 --> 00:04:41.751
And I started seeing myself
with a renewed sense of purpose --

00:04:42.419 --> 00:04:44.312
not as the old guy on the way out,

00:04:44.936 --> 00:04:46.650
but as someone with a role to play

00:04:46.674 --> 00:04:47.824
going forward.

00:04:49.770 --> 00:04:51.224
When I was growing up,

00:04:51.248 --> 00:04:53.780
life ended for most people in their 70s.

00:04:55.535 --> 00:04:57.359
People are living far longer now,

00:04:58.064 --> 00:05:00.211
and for the first time in human history,